'''休斯顿大学法律中心'''（University of Houston Law Center）是一所位于[[美国|美国]][[德克萨斯州|德克萨斯州]][[休斯顿|休斯顿]]的[[法学院|法学院]]，附属于[[休斯顿大学|休斯顿大学]]，创设于1947年。该院在《[[美国新闻与世界报道|美国新闻与世界报道]]》的[[美国法学院排名|法学院排名]]中排第58名。<ref name="University of Houston Law School">{{cite web | url=http://grad-schools.usnews.rankingsandreviews.com/best-graduate-schools/top-law-schools/university-of-houston-03154 | title=University of Houston > Law School | accessdate=2014-03-13 | archive-date=2016-09-29 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160929111915/http://grad-schools.usnews.rankingsandreviews.com/best-graduate-schools/top-law-schools/university-of-houston-03154 | dead-url=no }}</ref>
2005年[[2005年飓风卡特里娜|飓风卡特里娜]]袭击[[新奥尔良|新奥尔良]]的时候，该院接济了[[新奥尔良洛约拉大学法学院|新奥尔良洛约拉大学法学院]]全体师生，让他们能在异地继续进行教研。<ref>{{cite web|last=Willhoft|first=Ray|title=The Compassion of Neighbors, The Devotion of Community: Exiled School of Law Thrives During Challenging Times|url=http://www.loyno.edu/newsandcalendars/loyolatoday/index.php?action=view&article_id=81&issue_id=2&page=2&year=2006|publisher=[[Loyola_University_New_Orleans|Loyola University New Orleans]]|date=2006-01-06|accessdate=2007-11-15|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303194710/http://www.loyno.edu/newsandcalendars/loyolatoday/index.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>

